Package org.soulwing.prospecto

Static producers for various framework components
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Singleton<T>
    A factory that produces a singleton instance of a given type.
    UrlResolverProducer
    A singleton object that produces UrlResolver instances.
    ViewContextProducer
    A singleton object that produces ViewContext instances.
    ViewOptionsRegistry
    A static registry for view options.
    ViewReaderFactoryProducer
    A singleton object that produces ViewReaderFactory instances.
    ViewTemplateBuilderProducer
    A singleton object that produces ViewTemplateBuilder instances.
    ViewWriterFactoryProducer
    A singleton object that produces ViewWriterFactory instances.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NoSuchProviderException
    An exception thrown to indicate that a service provider was not found.
